  <Title>Darkages Futball League</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>&lt;b&gt;Teams:&lt;/b&gt;
Teams will consist of four individual aislings ((no multi-logging))

Teams will stay the same for the duration of the league (with the exception of the ALLSTAR match)

&lt;b&gt;Game Play:&lt;/b&gt;
The ball (a chosen aisling) starts in the center of the outlined playing field

The ball will always face the same direction as the team that is in control
If the ball lands on/outside of the designated playing field, it will be considered out of bounds and the other team gains control of the ball

Teammates can be used to assist in throwing the ball further

The number of throws per team is set����������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������������� on a match by match basis

For example, Team A may only have four throws at their disposal while Team B has 9. The max number of throws allowed for any one side at a time is 4.

The first team to score three (3) points will win the match

No shape-shifting of any kind (druid forms, insect/monster cloaks, etc)

&lt;b&gt;ALLSTARS:&lt;/b&gt;
To be eligible for an ALLSTAR team, you must have been part of a team that won five (5) or more matches

The two (2) players with the most scores during the duration of the league (15 matches total) will be selected as ALLSTAR team captains

ALLSTAR teams will be 6 vs 6 and the first team to five (5) points will be the winners

&lt;b&gt;Prizes:&lt;/b&gt;
For the duration of the league, each member of a winning team will be awarded a monetary prize

ALLSTAR prizes will be more substantial and will be announced at a later date.

((Darkages Futball League will be hosted by &lt;b&gt;Plebble&lt;/b&gt;. Please contact the Master Arena Host, Arena Hosts or Plebble for specific dates and times.))

</Content>
